            <title>[LU-12176] recovery-small test 107 fails with &apos;test_107 failed with 1&apos;</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12176</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;recovery-small test_107 fails, for far, for DNE testing with &apos;test_107 failed with 1&apos;. This test started failing on 8 April 2019. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looking at a recent failure at &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/29425f24-5a99-11e9-9720-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/29425f24-5a99-11e9-9720-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt; , the only sign of trouble in the suite_log is&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;mkdir: cannot create directory &apos;/mnt/lustre/d107.recovery-small/dir_106&apos;: Input/output error
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Looking at all the console logs, there&#8217;s nothing out of the ordinary that indicates a problem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Logs for recent failures are at&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/12aafa60-5a66-11e9-a256-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/12aafa60-5a66-11e9-a256-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
